<paragraph base="SL32750" id="IAS38_121" principles="no"><paranum>121</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 38"/><data name="paranum" value="121"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS38_P0341"><xref base="F16456357" href="../ias08/IAS08_TOC.dita#IAS08_TOC0001" id="IAS38_X0382">IAS 8</xref> requires an entity to disclose the nature and amount of a change in an accounting estimate  that has a material effect in the current period or is expected to have a material effect in subsequent periods. Such disclosure may arise from changes in: </p><ol base="SL142011" id="IAS38_L0040" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="SL142013" id="IAS38_P0342">the assessment of an <xref base="SL141716" href="IAS38_8.dita#IAS38_8/IAS38_P0070">intangible asset&#x2019;s<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0193"/></ph></xref> <xref base="SL141720" href="IAS38_8.dita#IAS38_8/IAS38_P0075">useful life<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0380"/></ph></xref>;</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="SL142015" id="IAS38_P0343">the <xref base="SL141702" href="IAS38_8.dita#IAS38_8/IAS38_P0057">amortisation<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0012"/></ph></xref> method; or</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p base="SL142017" id="IAS38_P0344"><xref base="SL141719" href="IAS38_8.dita#IAS38_8/IAS38_P0074">residual values<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0335"/></ph></xref>.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>